They go to the forest. The dog see bumblebees. The little boy look down in a hole. The dog play with the bumblebees. He try to catch them.

The boy say 'Frog, where are you?' A prairie dog hit him in the nose. The dog howl at the bumblebees. The bumblebees chase the dog.

The boy climb on a big rock. He say 'Frog, where are you?' He get stuck on a deer's head. The deer run. The dog come with him.

The deer stop at the cliff. Down go the boy and the dog. They go in the water. Splash.

The boy hear something. He say 'Shh' to the dog. They look on the other side of the log. They see mommy frog and daddy frog. They see little frog's family.

They take little frog. They say goodbye to the family. They go home. The little boy and the dog happy.
